	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1" facs="R 87-11 17 (43)"/>
			<p>“A prominent <term ref="#ehri_dr_gentile">non-Jewish</term>
				<term ref="#ehri_dr_nationalities_bulgarians">Bulgarian</term> member of the <orgName
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-005034">Bulgarian Parliament</orgName> has come to <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/745044/istanbul.html">Istanbul</placeName> especially to make strong personal representations upon
				humanitarian grounds in influential quarters regarding the condition of the <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> in <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/732800/republic-of-bulgaria.html">Bulgaria</placeName>. [...] This informant says that the entire
					<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-872" type="subject">Jewish community</term> in <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/732800/republic-of-bulgaria.html">Bulgaria</placeName> is <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-662" type="subject">threatened</term> with immediate <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-601" type="subject">destruction</term>. <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/732800/republic-of-bulgaria.html">Bulgarian </placeName><term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews </term>are now in a much worse situation than
				those in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/798549/romania.html">Rumania</placeName> and <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/719819/hungary.html">Hungary</placeName>. Nothing can be done for the <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews </term>from <term
					ref="#ehri_dr_nationalities_bulgarians">Bulgarian</term>occupied <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/738770/thrace.html"
					>Thrace</placeName> and <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/718075/republic-of-macedonia.html">Macedonia</placeName>, for all
				of them including <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826" type="subject">men</term>, <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">women</term> and <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-824" type="subject">children</term> will be <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">deported</term> to <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/798544/republic-of-poland.html">Poland</placeName> and their <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">deportation</term> has already begun.</p>
			<p>He adds that the intention of the <orgName ref="#ehri_dr_government_bulgarian">Bulgarian Government</orgName> is to <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">deport</term> to <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/798544/republic-of-poland.html">Poland</placeName> all <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> in <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/732800/republic-of-bulgaria.html">Bulgaria</placeName> and an <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-339" type="subject">order</term> for this purpose has been issued. Owing
				to <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-257" type="subject">popular protests</term>
				<pb n="2" facs="R 87-11 17 (44)"/> led by prominent <term ref="#ehri_dr_gentile">non-Jewish</term>
				<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/732800/republic-of-bulgaria.html">Bulgarian</placeName> citizens this order has been stayed
				temporarily but not rescinded.</p>
			<p>The <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-594" type="subject">policy</term> of <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-529" type="subject">extermination</term> he states is demanded by the
					<term ref="#ehri_dr_nationalities_germans">Germans</term> and promoted by <persName
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_pers-000132">Gabrovski</persName>. The lives of 45,000 <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term>are at stake. The parliamentarian declares
				that in his opinion the most effective way to <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-296" type="subject"
					>help</term> them is for the <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-1331">United States
					Government</orgName> to make a vigorous <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-257" type="subject"
					>protest</term> to the <orgName ref="#ehri_dr_government_bulgarian">Bulgarian Government</orgName> through the <placeName
					ref="http://www.geonames.org/2658434/switzerland.html">Swiss</placeName> authorities declaring in the strongest terms its
				abhorrence of the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-594" type="subject">policy</term> of the <orgName
					ref="#ehri_dr_government_bulgarian">Bulgarian Government</orgName> toward the <term
					ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term>.”</p>
